<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ka Pathien Ngei Na Hi</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka pa na hi ka Pathien ngei na hi,
 Leia zinmang suoka ka tan laiin;
 Na hehpihna thimthu a hung tunga,
 &quot;Hung kitin ka hun tan zo tai&quot; tiin.

[V2]
 Na hehpihna thupiek zawp chu,
 Lung kisik a um ngei puoi Lalpa;
 Sietlei leh thangvan a mi le.

[V3]
 2. Aw Lalpa Na vangsakna lopi hi,
 Nang sangin zatam in a ngailul zawu;
 Taksap vanga luonthi a naihlai in,
 Na gam leh Na felna'n ei gamlat ki'n.

[V4]
 Nang ngei Isu ka hun neih chun,
 Bang dang ka ngai ta dem maw Lalpa;
 Bangkima ka bangkim Na hi.

[V5]
 3. Nawpna hawlin a vak ui sang tamtak,
 Mu loin than thim sungah a liem ui;
 Lopina lim a delh uh lei nawpna,
 Mu leh changte di'n kumsawt a ting puoi.

[V6]
 Nang ngei Isu neih tak Na hi,
 Kumsawt chana lopi leh hawih deuh deuh;
 Lei leh vana vangsakna lul.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>127</hymn_number>
<author>Thangngur</author>
</song>